					.product__item-count.count
						button.count__minus
						input(type='text' value=0).count__current
						button.count__plus +
					.product__item-price 300p.
					button.product__item-add Добавить в корзину
				.product__item(data-id="3")
					.product__item-image
						img(src='@img/tempura.jpg').product__item-img
					h3.product__item-title Темпура
					.product__item-count.count
						button.count__minus
						input(type='text' value=0).count__current
						button.count__plus +
